Classes in compiler used by compiler
Block
          A block consisting of zero or more statements.
Expression
          An expression consisting of a single Term, followed by zero or more ADDOP TERM pairs.
Factor
          A factor consisting of a single expression object encapsulated in parentheses OR a DIGITS as defined by Token OR an IDENTIFIER as defined by Token
GameFunction
          GameCommand is a class that holds the Game Function itself, as defined by Token and the parameters to that game function call.
MainProgram
          A block of MAIN{} code with any number of statements between the opening and closing braces
Parameters
          An ordered list of parameters.
Statement
          A STATEMENT is an object that is nested inside of Blocks.
Subroutine
          A SUBROUTINE consisting of the subroutine's IDENTIFIER as defined by Token and it's parameter list Also contains the subroutine's Block of code.
Term
          A term consisting of a single Factor, followed by zero or more MULTOP FACTOR pairs.
TextFile
          Wrapper class that is used to pull a text file from hard disk into memory.
Token
          Tokens are built from terminal symbols in the Robot Wars language.
Token.TokenType
          Collection of token types.
